{"tid":804590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(時光旅行者) 習近平變成開國領袖","createTime":"2018-09-03T06:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T09:01:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":62,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"069844ec8f63a0518bb9f3841044b08db977e95c","tid":804590,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpEgoJ4F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpEgoJ4F.jpg&h=95e78251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國深圳蛇口改革開放博物館先前重新開幕，館內「開國領袖」塑像只剩下毛澤東，原本擺放鄧小平塑像的位置則被習近平取代，網友對於出生於1953年的習近平，能成為1949中國建國的開國領袖，直呼「居然跟死人搶位置，也算是千古奇葩」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，2018年為中國前領導人鄧小平改革開放40週年，深圳蛇口改革開放博物館對此在今年6月關閉裝修，在8月10日重新開張，館內原本擺放的開國領袖鄧小平塑像不見蹤影，只剩下毛澤東塑像且新增習近平塑像，還有一整面載有習近平語錄的牆壁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2535263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2535263&d=B77mozuHgSHAw5Nhb0exGi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b0a95fbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2535263&h=cc93a42f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2535263</a>"},{"pid":"a7275e7108092cc051b8a00ae55c03a81fede9b7","tid":804590,"uid":164730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"069844ec8f63a0518bb9f3841044b08db977e95c","tid":804590,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpEgoJ4F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpEgoJ4F.jpg&h=95e78251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國深圳蛇口改革開放博物館先前重新開幕，館內「開國領袖」塑像只剩下毛澤東，原本擺放鄧小平塑像的位置則被習近平取代，網友對於出生於1953年的習近平，能成為1949中國建國的開國領袖，直呼「居然跟死人搶位置，也算是千古奇葩」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，2018年為中國前領導人鄧小平改革開放40週年，深圳蛇口改革開放博物館對此在今年6月關閉裝修，在8月10日重新開張，館內原本擺放的開國領袖鄧小平塑像不見蹤影，只剩下毛澤東塑像且新增習近平塑像，還有一整面載有習近平語錄的牆壁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2535263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2535263&d=B77mozuHgSHAw5Nhb0exGi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b0a95fbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2535263&h=cc93a42f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2535263</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:46:34.000Z","msg":"去鄧化"},{"pid":"d538e67d494686239693461a9daed026fa4be8c1","tid":804590,"uid":149844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:48:18.000Z","msg":"習近平稱%#～&yen;+"},{"pid":"9e666cfb000e8f849493c2ec6a1ae6362f60227b","tid":804590,"uid":38173,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:48:42.000Z","msg":"冥幣幾時改埋做雜帝個乜頭  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab4fdcfe023791c557dfe03299c7b221991e320","tid":804590,"uid":68215,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:51:17.000Z","msg":"天安門幾時會掛習總張相"},{"pid":"5a25af4caa6f8d7d6fed8fcf05172301ccd55b1f","tid":804590,"uid":40624,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:53:15.000Z","msg":"愈黎愈似1984<br />\n真理部, 2+2=5"},{"pid":"3a07e39bf041e9ba3965e824a92c6774d444a953","tid":804590,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"新中國要黎喇"},{"pid":"631018769026237daba1ac0034e88c5ddde8bb0d","tid":804590,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:39:16.000Z","msg":"大陸係咪已經發明到時光機去改寫歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0d1e0b0b10db3552fd17720f1678ae2011d650","tid":804590,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:4